交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests #Chinazi<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uC3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=458527c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour <br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.06"},{"pid":"5ebf65a1c1cf40aa11749a21bc2e10ebd2655d45","tid":1549712,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:37:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa56468ed08d03860e1305e6209a831c0b75c510","tid":1549712,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70639fcf997cfcd46aa63c55a97afa3172d67349","tid":1549712,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12d11ec5a174d2e054d95ea479c3c469ca8e73e","tid":1549712,"uid":40902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:43:12.000Z","msg":"想自己print國旗的手足注意<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NAehJf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNAehJf8.jpg&h=15a8156d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DW6jWA9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDW6jWA9.jpg&h=389e6260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X5vEb9u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX5vEb9u.jpg&h=84e293c6&s={SIZE